michael e dyson , department of sociology , georgetown university described by michael a. fletcher as " a princeton ph . d. and a child of the streets who takes pains never to separate the two " , dyson has authored or edited 18 books dealing with subjects such as malcolm x , martin luther king , jr. , marvin gaye , nas 's debut album illmatic , bill cosby , tupac shakur and hurricane katrina .

bio subjects : michael eric dyson analyzes this real man , not just his image as mythic minister & leader , in " i may not get there with you "

